{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775863665788,"sessionID":"ses_286474d8fffeKqLRB2b8M5keEa","part":{"id":"prt_d79b91121001s55jo3IFOLLFn9","messageID":"msg_d79b9027b001oDA0bqNrssxOAk","sessionID":"ses_286474d8fffeKqLRB2b8M5keEa","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_4f798a37119141a0999148b3","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-002: CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n2: \n3: **Module:** pkg/apis  \n4: **Language:** Go  \n5: **Size:** S  \n6: **Design Stage:** ST-3 completed\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Tasks\n11: \n12: - [ ] **T1** Define `CodeInterpreter` CRD type struct with embedded TypeMeta and ObjectMeta  \n13:   - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`  \n14:   - Verify: Type struct includes `Spec` and `Status` fields with appropriate JSON tags\n15: \n16: - [ ] **T2** Add kubebuilder markers for CodeInterpreter  \n17:   - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`  \n18:   - Markers: `+genclient`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`, `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`, `+kubebuilder:resource:shortName=ci`  \n19:   - Verify: Markers present above type definition\n20: \n21: - [ ] **T3** Define `CodeInterpreterList` list type  \n22:   - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`  \n23:   - Verify: List type embeds TypeMeta, ListMeta and contains `Items []CodeInterpreter`\n24: \n25: - [ ] **T4** Define `CodeInterpreterSpec` spec struct  \n26:   - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`  \n27:   - Fields: AuthMode, MaxSessionDuration, SessionTimeout, Ports, Template, WarmPoolSize  \n28:   - Verify: All fields with appropriate kubebuilder validation markers\n29: \n30: - [ ] **T5** Define `CodeInterpreterStatus` status struct  \n31:   - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`  \n32:   - Fields: Conditions, ObservedGeneration, Ready  \n33:   - Verify: Status struct follows standard Kubernetes status pattern\n34: \n35: - [ ] **T6** Define `AuthMode` enum type and constants  \n36:   - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`  \n37:   - Constants: `AuthModePicod = \"picod\"`, `AuthModeNone = \"none\"`  \n38:   - Verify: Enum with +kubebuilder:validation:Enum marker\n39: \n40: - [ ] **T7** Define `ContainerTemplateSpec` supporting type  \n41:   - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`  \n42:   - Fields: Image, Command, Args, Env, Resources, RuntimeClassName  \n43:   - Verify: Required Image field with proper markers\n44: \n45: - [ ] **T8** Add CodeInterpreter types to register.go  \n46:   - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go`  \n47:   - Add `&CodeInterpreter{}` and `&CodeInterpreterList{}` to AddKnownTypes  \n48:   - Verify: Both types registered in scheme\n49: \n50: - [ ] **T9** Generate DeepCopy methods  \n51:   - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`  \n52:   - Use: `controller-gen object paths=./pkg/apis/...`  \n53:   - Verify: DeepCopyInto and DeepCopy methods generated for all types\n54: \n55: - [ ] **T10** Write unit tests for CodeInterpreter types  \n56:   - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`  \n57:   - Coverage: Type instantiation, DeepCopy, defaults validation  \n58:   - Verify: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...` passes\n59: \n60: - [ ] **T11** Verify types compile correctly  \n61:   - Command: `go build ./pkg/apis/...`  \n62:   - Verify: No compilation errors\n63: \n64: - [ ] **T12** Run linter on API types  \n65:   - Command: `golangci-lint run ./pkg/apis/...` or `go vet ./pkg/apis/...`  \n66:   - Verify: No linting errors\n67: \n68: ---\n69: \n70: ## Dependencies\n71: \n72: ```\n73: T1 → T2 → T3 → T4 → T5 → T6 → T7 → T8 → T9 → T10 → T11 → T12\n74: ```\n75: \n76: **Parallel:** T6, T7 can be done in parallel with T4, T5\n77: \n78: ## Acceptance Criteria\n79: \n80: - [ ] CodeInterpreter CRD type defined in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n81: - [ ] CodeInterpreter includes spec: authMode, maxSessionDuration, sessionTimeout, ports, template, warmPoolSize\n82: - [ ] CodeInterpreter includes status: conditions, observedGeneration, ready\n83: - [ ] All types implement `runtime.Object` interface\n84: - [ ] DeepCopy methods generated and compile correctly\n85: - [ ] `go build ./pkg/apis/...` passes\n86: - [ ] `go vet ./pkg/apis/...` passes\n87: - [ ] Unit tests pass\n88: \n89: ---\n90: \n91: # AR-003: CRD 共享类型与常量\n92: \n93: **Module:** pkg/apis  \n94: **Language:** Go  \n95: **Size:** S  \n96: **Design Stage:** ST-3 completed\n97: \n98: ---\n99: \n100: ## Tasks\n101: \n102: - [ ] **T1** 定义 `TargetPort` 共享结构体（端口配置）\n103:   - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n104:   - 字段: Port, Protocol, Name, PathPrefix\n105:   - 验证: 类型定义正确，JSON tag 完整\n106: \n107: - [ ] **T2** 定义 `PodTemplateSpec` 共享结构体（Pod 模板）\n108:   - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n109:   - 验证: 嵌入 metav1.ObjectMeta，可选 Spec 引用 PodSpec\n110: \n111: - [ ] **T3** 定义 `PodSpec` 共享结构体（Pod 规范子集）\n112:   - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n113:   - 字段: Containers, Volumes, RestartPolicy, ServiceAccountName, NodeSelector, Affinity, Tolerations 等\n114:   - 验证: 所有字段正确从 corev1.PodSpec 引用\n115: \n116: - [ ] **T4** 定义 `ContainerSpec` 共享结构体（容器规范子集）\n117:   - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n118:   - 字段: Name, Image, Command, Args, Env, Resources, Ports 等\n119:   - 验证: 包含容器核心字段\n120: \n121: - [ ] **T5** 定义 `AuthMode` 类型及常量\n122:   - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n123:   - 常量: `AuthModePicod = \"picod\"`, `AuthModeNone = \"none\"`\n124:   - 验证: 类型定义和常量值正确\n125: \n126: - [ ] **T6** 为 TargetPort 添加 kubebuilder 验证标记\n127:   - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n128:   - 验证: Port 范围 1-65535, Protocol 枚举 HTTP/HTTPS\n129: \n130: - [ ] **T7** 为 PodSpec 字段添加可选标记\n131:   - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n132:   - 验证: 所有字段标记 +optional\n133: \n134: - [ ] **T8** 为 ContainerSpec 字段添加验证标记\n135:   - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n136:   - 验证: Name 和 Image 标记为 required\n137: \n138: - [ ] **T9** 运行 deep copy 生成\n139:   - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n140:   - 命令: `controller-gen object paths=./pkg/apis/...`\n141:   - 验证: 所有共享类型的 DeepCopy 方法已生成\n142: \n143: - [ ] **T10** 验证共享类型编译正确\n144:   - 命令: `go build ./pkg/apis/...`\n145:   - 验证: 无编译错误\n146: \n147: - [ ] **T11** 运行 linter 检查\n148:   - 命令: `go vet ./pkg/apis/...`\n149:   - 验证: 无 lint 错误\n150: \n151: - [ ] **T12** 编写共享类型单元测试\n152:   - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n153:   - 验证: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...` 通过\n154: \n155: ---\n156: \n157: ## 依赖关系\n158: \n159: ```\n160: T1 ─┬─> T6 ─> T9 ─> T10 ─> T11 ─> T12\n161: T2 ─┤\n162: T3 ─┤\n163: T4 ─┤\n164: T5 ─┘\n165: T7 ─> T9\n166: T8 ─> T9\n167: ```\n168: \n169: **并行:** T2, T3, T4, T5 可并行执行\n170: \n171: ## 验收标准\n172: \n173: - [ ] TargetPort, PodTemplateSpec, PodSpec, ContainerSpec 共享类型已定义\n174: - [ ] AuthMode 类型及常量已定义\n175: - [ ] 所有类型包含正确的 kubebuilder 验证标记\n176: - [ ] DeepCopy 方法已生成并编译正确\n177: - [ ] `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 通过\n178: - [ ] `go vet ./pkg/apis/...` 通过\n179: - [ ] 单元测试通过\n180: \n181: ---\n182: \n183: # AR-008: Sandbox GC 定时清理机制 (Sandbox GC Timing Cleanup Mechanism)\n184: \n185: **Module:** pkg/workloadmanager  \n186: **Language:** Go  \n187: **Size:** S  \n188: **Design Stage:** ST-3 completed (design in `pkg/workloadmanager/design.md`)\n189: \n190: ---\n191: \n192: ## Tasks\n193: \n194: ### Phase 1: Core Data Structures\n195: \n196: - [ ] **T-001** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/gc.go` with GCConfig struct (Interval, BatchSize, MaxConcurrentDeletes, GracePeriod, EnableMetrics)\n197: - [ ] **T-002** Implement DefaultGCConfig() function with sensible defaults (5m interval, 50 batch, 10 concurrent, 30s grace)\n198: - [ ] **T-003** Create GCWorker struct with client, k8sClient, config, stopCh, cleanupMgr, expirationChecker fields\n199: - [ ] **T-004** Implement GCResult struct (ScannedCount, ExpiredCount, DeletedCount, FailedCount, Duration, Errors)\n200: - [ ] **T-005** Implement GCStats struct (TotalCycles, TotalDeleted, TotalFailed, LastRunTime, LastResult)\n201: \n202: ### Phase 2: GC Worker Core\n203: \n204: - [ ] **T-006** Implement NewGCWorker() constructor function\n205: - [ ] **T-007** Implement GCWorker.Start(ctx) with ticker-based scheduling\n206: - [ ] **T-008** Implement GCWorker.Stop() method\n207: - [ ] **T-009** Implement GCWorker.runGCCycle() - main GC cycle logic\n208: - [ ] **T-010** Implement GCWorker.getNamespaces() to list target namespaces\n209: - [ ] **T-011** Implement GCWorker.processNamespace() to scan and delete expired resources in a namespace\n210: \n211: ### Phase 3: Expiration Detection & Deletion\n212: \n213: - [ ] **T-012** Implement GCWorker.isExpired(*AgentRuntime) using expiration.go logic\n214: - [ ] **T-013** Implement GCWorker.isExpired(*CodeInterpreter) using expiration.go logic\n215: - [ ] **T-014** Implement GCWorker.getLastActivityTime() to extract from annotations\n216: - [ ] **T-015** Implement GCWorker.deleteAgentRuntime() with CleanupManager integration\n217: - [ ] **T-016** Implement GCWorker.deleteCodeInterpreter() with CleanupManager integration\n218: \n219: ### Phase 4: HTTP API Integration\n220: \n221: - [ ] **T-017** Implement GCServer wrapper struct\n222: - [ ] **T-018** Implement GCTriggerResponse, GCStatusResponse, GCConfigUpdateRequest types\n223: - [ ] **T-019** Implement NewGCServer() constructor\n224: - [ ] **T-020** Implement GCServer.RegisterRoutes() with /gc/* endpoints\n225: - [ ] **T-021** Implement handleTrigger() - POST /api/v1/gc/trigger\n226: - [ ] **T-022** Implement handleStatus() - GET /api/v1/gc/status\n227: - [ ] **T-023** Implement handleConfigUpdate() - PUT /api/v1/gc/config\n228: \n229: ### Phase 5: Configuration & Integration\n230: \n231: - [ ] **T-024** Add GCConfig to server Config struct\n232: - [ ] **T-025** Load GC config from environment variables (GC_INTERVAL, GC_BATCH_SIZE, GC_MAX_CONCURRENT_DELETES, GC_GRACE_PERIOD, GC_ENABLED)\n233: - [ ] **T-026** Initialize and start GC worker in server startup\n234: - [ ] **T-027** Register GC routes in server router setup\n235: \n236: ### Phase 6: Testing\n237: \n238: - [ ] **T-028** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/gc_test.go`\n239: - [ ] **T-029** Write unit test: TestGCWorkerIsExpired_* (with DeletionTimestamp, TTL, idle timeout)\n240: - [ ] **T-030** Write unit test: TestGCConfig validation\n241: - [ ] **T-031** Write unit test: TestGCWorkerGetNamespaces\n242: - [ ] **T-032** Write unit test: TestGCWorkerStartStop\n243: - [ ] **T-033** Write unit test: TestGCServerRoutes\n244: \n245: ### Phase 7: Documentation & Cleanup\n246: \n247: - [ ] **T-034** Add error variables (ErrGCWorkerNotRunning, ErrGCAlreadyRunning, ErrInvalidConfig)\n248: - [ ] **T-035** Add logging at appropriate levels (V(4) cycle, V(2) failures, V(1) config)\n249: - [ ] **T-036** Verify code compiles: `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...`\n250: - [ ] **T-037** Run tests: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v`\n251: - [ ] **T-038** Verify 80% test coverage for gc.go\n\n(End of file - total 251 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-002: CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n\n**Module:** pkg/apis  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S  \n**Design Stage:** ST-3 completed\n\n---\n\n## Tasks\n\n- [ ] **T1** Define `CodeInterpreter` CRD type struct with embedded TypeMeta and ObjectMeta  \n  - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`  \n  - Verify: Type struct includes `Spec` and `Status` fields with appropriate JSON tags\n\n- [ ] **T2** Add kubebuilder markers for CodeInterpreter  \n  - File: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`  \n  - Markers: `+genclient`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`, `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`, `+kubebuilder:resource:shortName=ci`  \n  - Verify: Markers present above type definition\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775863665780,"end":1775863665786}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775863665815,"sessionID":"ses_286474d8fffeKqLRB2b8M5keEa","part":{"id":"prt_d79b9147b001lcyB94QBt5X48c","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d79b9027b001oDA0bqNrssxOAk","sessionID":"ses_286474d8fffeKqLRB2b8M5keEa","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":36399,"input":3845,"output":172,"reasoning":0,"cache":{"write":0,"read":32382}},"cost":0}}
